snippet.title: 21 Jump Street - Tracy admits to lying about rape [3x01]
snippet.description:
Tracy Edwards (Lossen Chambers) confesses to Hansen (Johnny Depp) that she never was raped and that the bruises were from a fight with a girl named Jackie (Daya Faye).

S3E1 - Fun With Animals (21 Jump Street FOX)
